Both bugs fixed and verified:

**Fixes Applied:**

| File | Bug | Root Cause | Fix |
|------|-----|------------|-----|
| `job_queue.py:24-26` | Duplicate processing | `await` between status check and update let all workers see "pending" before any claimed it | Set status to "processing" atomically before the `await` |
| `worker.py:19-20` | Vanishing failures | Exception handler only logged, never called `queue.fail()` | Added `queue.fail(job["id"], str(e))` |

